    • BuildInfo

      public BuildInfo(int id, PushPayload.Sender sender, List<PushPayload.Commit> commitList, BuildInfo.BuildDetails buildDetails, BuildInfo.TestDetails testDetails, String buildDate, String branch)
      Creates a new BuildInfo object.
      Parameters:
      id - Build id
      sender - Sender of push payload that triggered CI build
      commitList - List of commits associated with push payload
      buildDetails - Details on build, including result and logs
      testDetails - Details on test, including total tests, number of tests passed and logs
      buildDate - Date of build as string
      branch - Branch of the build
